Instance types:
 OnDemand:  Use and Pay
 Reserved:   Pay and Use
 Spot:       Bidding
 Dedicated:  Dedicated Hardware will be allocated to that particular instance.
 Dedicated Host: complete hardware will be allocated to that host and it is so expensive
